             was indicted for <rs id="t17930911-33-off182" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930911-33-off182" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930911-33-off182" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930911-33-victim371" type="victimName">
                           Alexander 
                           Peffers
                        <interp inst="t17930911-33-victim371" type="surname" value="Peffers"></interp>
