                   about the hours of nine in the night on the <rs id="t17930911-33-cd183" type="crimeDate">5th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930911-33-off182 t17930911-33-cd183"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, a wooden box, value 6 d. a pair of linen sheets, value 1 s. a muslin apron, value 8 d. three pair of worsted stockings, value 1 s. and a dimity waistcoat, value 6 d. the goods of the said 
                     <persName id="t17930911-33-person372">
                        Alexander
                         Peffers
